ipv6IcmpMIB.description: The MIB module for entities implementing the ICMPv6.

ipv6IfIcmpTable.name: ipv6IfIcmpTable
ipv6IfIcmpTable.description: IPv6 ICMP statistics. This table contains statistics of ICMPv6 messages that are received and sourced by the entity.

ipv6IfIcmpEntry.name: ipv6IfIcmpEntry
ipv6IfIcmpEntry.description: An ICMPv6 statistics entry containing objects at a particular IPv6 interface. Note that a receiving interface is the interface to which a given ICMPv6 message is addressed which may not be necessarily the input interface for the message. Similarly, the sending interface is the interface that sources a given ICMP message which is usually but not necessarily the output interface for the message.

ipv6IfIcmpInMsgs.name: ipv6IfIcmpInMsgs
ipv6IfIcmpInMsgs.description: The total number of ICMP messages received by the interface which includes all those counted by ipv6IfIcmpInErrors. Note that this interface is the interface to which the ICMP messages were addressed which may not be necessarily the input interface for the messages.

ipv6IfIcmpInErrors.name: ipv6IfIcmpInErrors
ipv6IfIcmpInErrors.description: The number of ICMP messages which the interface received but determined as having ICMP-specific errors (bad ICMP checksums, bad length, etc.).

ipv6IfIcmpInDestUnreachs.name: ipv6IfIcmpInDestUnreachs
ipv6IfIcmpInDestUnreachs.description: The number of ICMP Destination Unreachable messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpInAdminProhibs.name: ipv6IfIcmpInAdminProhibs
ipv6IfIcmpInAdminProhibs.description: The number of ICMP destination unreachable/communication administratively prohibited messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpInTimeExcds.name: ipv6IfIcmpInTimeExcds
ipv6IfIcmpInTimeExcds.description: The number of ICMP Time Exceeded messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpInParmProblems.name: ipv6IfIcmpInParmProblems
ipv6IfIcmpInParmProblems.description: The number of ICMP Parameter Problem messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpInPktTooBigs.name: ipv6IfIcmpInPktTooBigs
ipv6IfIcmpInPktTooBigs.description: The number of ICMP Packet Too Big messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpInEchos.name: ipv6IfIcmpInEchos
ipv6IfIcmpInEchos.description: The number of ICMP Echo (request) messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpInEchoReplies.name: ipv6IfIcmpInEchoReplies
ipv6IfIcmpInEchoReplies.description: The number of ICMP Echo Reply messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpInRouterSolicits.name: ipv6IfIcmpInRouterSolicits
ipv6IfIcmpInRouterSolicits.description: The number of ICMP Router Solicit messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpInRouterAdvertisements.name: ipv6IfIcmpInRouterAdvertisements
ipv6IfIcmpInRouterAdvertisements.description: The number of ICMP Router Advertisement messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpInNeighborSolicits.name: ipv6IfIcmpInNeighborSolicits
ipv6IfIcmpInNeighborSolicits.description: The number of ICMP Neighbor Solicit messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpInNeighborAdvertisements.name: ipv6IfIcmpInNeighborAdvertisements
ipv6IfIcmpInNeighborAdvertisements.description: The number of ICMP Neighbor Advertisement messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpInRedirects.name: ipv6IfIcmpInRedirects
ipv6IfIcmpInRedirects.description: The number of Redirect messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpInGroupMembQueries.name: ipv6IfIcmpInGroupMembQueries
ipv6IfIcmpInGroupMembQueries.description: The number of ICMPv6 Group Membership Query messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpInGroupMembResponses.name: ipv6IfIcmpInGroupMembResponses
ipv6IfIcmpInGroupMembResponses.description: The number of ICMPv6 Group Membership Response messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpInGroupMembReductions.name: ipv6IfIcmpInGroupMembReductions
ipv6IfIcmpInGroupMembReductions.description: The number of ICMPv6 Group Membership Reduction messages received by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpOutMsgs.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutMsgs
ipv6IfIcmpOutMsgs.description: The total number of ICMP messages which this interface attempted to send. Note that this counter includes all those counted by icmpOutErrors.

ipv6IfIcmpOutErrors.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutErrors
ipv6IfIcmpOutErrors.description: The number of ICMP messages which this interface did not send due to problems discovered within ICMP such as a lack of buffers. This value should not include errors discovered outside the ICMP layer such as the inability of IPv6 to route the resultant datagram. In some implementations there may be no types of error which contribute to this counter's value.

ipv6IfIcmpOutDestUnreachs.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutDestUnreachs
ipv6IfIcmpOutDestUnreachs.description: The number of ICMP Destination Unreachable messages sent by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpOutAdminProhibs.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutAdminProhibs
ipv6IfIcmpOutAdminProhibs.description: Number of ICMP dest unreachable/communication administratively prohibited messages sent.

ipv6IfIcmpOutTimeExcds.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutTimeExcds
ipv6IfIcmpOutTimeExcds.description: The number of ICMP Time Exceeded messages sent by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpOutParmProblems.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutParmProblems
ipv6IfIcmpOutParmProblems.description: The number of ICMP Parameter Problem messages sent by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpOutPktTooBigs.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutPktTooBigs
ipv6IfIcmpOutPktTooBigs.description: The number of ICMP Packet Too Big messages sent by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpOutEchos.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutEchos
ipv6IfIcmpOutEchos.description: The number of ICMP Echo (request) messages sent by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpOutEchoReplies.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutEchoReplies
ipv6IfIcmpOutEchoReplies.description: The number of ICMP Echo Reply messages sent by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpOutRouterSolicits.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutRouterSolicits
ipv6IfIcmpOutRouterSolicits.description: The number of ICMP Router Solicitation messages sent by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpOutRouterAdvertisements.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutRouterAdvertisements
ipv6IfIcmpOutRouterAdvertisements.description: The number of ICMP Router Advertisement messages sent by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpOutNeighborSolicits.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutNeighborSolicits
ipv6IfIcmpOutNeighborSolicits.description: The number of ICMP Neighbor Solicitation messages sent by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpOutNeighborAdvertisements.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutNeighborAdvertisements
ipv6IfIcmpOutNeighborAdvertisements.description: The number of ICMP Neighbor Advertisement messages sent by the interface.

ipv6IfIcmpOutRedirects.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutRedirects
ipv6IfIcmpOutRedirects.description: The number of Redirect messages sent. For a host, this object will always be zero, since hosts do not send redirects.

ipv6IfIcmpOutGroupMembQueries.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutGroupMembQueries
ipv6IfIcmpOutGroupMembQueries.description: The number of ICMPv6 Group Membership Query messages sent.

ipv6IfIcmpOutGroupMembResponses.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutGroupMembResponses
ipv6IfIcmpOutGroupMembResponses.description: The number of ICMPv6 Group Membership Response messages sent.

ipv6IfIcmpOutGroupMembReductions.name: ipv6IfIcmpOutGroupMembReductions
ipv6IfIcmpOutGroupMembReductions.description: The number of ICMPv6 Group Membership Reduction messages sent.

ipv6IcmpCompliance.name: ipv6IcmpCompliance
ipv6IcmpCompliance.description: The compliance statement for SNMPv2 entities which implement ICMPv6.

ipv6IcmpGroup.name: ipv6IcmpGroup
ipv6IcmpGroup.description: The ICMPv6 group of objects providing information specific to ICMPv6.
